{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag"},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSTag","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":[{"name":"iOS","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"15.0"},{"name":"macOS","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"13.0"},{"name":"tvOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"16.0"},{"name":"visionOS","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"1.0"},{"name":"watchOS","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"11.0"}],"title":"OUDSTag","roleHeading":"Structure","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents7OUDSTagV","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSTag","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"struct"},"abstract":[{"text":"Tag is a UI element that allows to display short info like a label, keyword, or category.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Tag helps users quickly find, group, or understand content.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudstag"]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/Status"],"generated":true,"title":"Structures","anchor":"Structures"},{"title":"Initializers","generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/init(_:tableName:bundle:status:appearance:shape:size:hasLoader:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/init(label:status:appearance:shape:size:hasLoader:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/init(loadingKey:tableName:bundle:shape:size:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/init(loadingLabel:shape:size:)"]},{"title":"Instance Properties","generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/body"]},{"generated":true,"title":"Enumerations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/Appearance","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/Shape","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/Size"],"anchor":"Enumerations"},{"title":"Default Implementations","generated":true,"anchor":"Default-Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/View-Implementations"]}],"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSTag","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Indicators"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Appearances","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Appearances"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Tags have two appearances so as to highlight or not their content:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"emphasized","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with a solid, high-contrast background. Used to draw strong attention to important"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"labels or categories. Emphasized tags stand out prominently against the interface and are ideal for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"primary or high-priority information.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"muted"}]},{"text":": A tag with a subtle, light, or semi-transparent background. Used for secondary or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"less prominent information. Muted tags blend more with the background, providing a softer visual","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"emphasis compared to emphasized tags.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Status","anchor":"Status","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags have seven status depending on the context of the information they represent. Each state is designed"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to convey a specific meaning and ensure clarity in communication."}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Neutral"}]},{"text":": Default or inactive state. Used for standard labels, categories, or when no specific","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"status needs to be communicated.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Accent"}]},{"text":": Used to draw attention to new features, recommendations, or content suggestions.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Invites users to explore and engage with new offerings, creating an exciting and engaging experience.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Positive"}]},{"text":": Indicates success, confirmation, or a positive status. Commonly used to highlight","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"completed actions or approved items.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Warning"}]},{"text":": Signals caution or a potentially risky situation. Used to draw attention to items","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"requiring user awareness or intervention.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Negative","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Represents errors, critical issues, or urgent attention needed. Used to highlight"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"problems or failed actions.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Info"}]},{"text":": Conveys informational messages or supplementary details. Used for neutral, helpful,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or contextual information."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Disabled"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Shows that the tag is inactive and cannot be interacted with. Appears faded or greyed out. This is not"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"allowed when loader is activated."}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Shape","anchor":"Shape","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags can have two shapes:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Rounded"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with fully rounded corners, creating a pill-shaped appearance. Rounded"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"tags offer a softer and more approachable look, suitable for most modern interfaces."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Square"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with sharp, square corners. Squared tags provide a more formal, structured, or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"technical feel. They are often used in business contexts to label promotions, offers, or important notices."}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Size","anchor":"Size"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Tags can have two sizes:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Default","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": The standard tag size, suitable for most use cases and offering good readability."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Small","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A compact tag with reduced height and font size. Used when saving space is important or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when grouping elements visually."}]}]}]},{"anchor":"Layout","text":"Layout","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"There are four available layouts for tags:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Text only"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag that displays only text. Used for simple labels, categories, or keywords without additional visual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"elements."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Text + Bullet"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag with a small indicator (dot) alongside the text. Used to show status, presence, or activity"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"next to the label."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"-"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Text + Icon"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag that includes an icon before the text. Used to visually reinforce the meaning of the tag,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as status, type, or action."}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Text + Loader","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": A tag that combines a loading spinner (or progress indicator) with text. Used to indicate that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a process or action related to the tag is in progress."}]}]}]},{"anchor":"Code-samples","text":"Code samples","type":"heading","level":2},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Text only with neutral status, for emphasized appearance with rounded shape in default size","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\",  status: .neutral(), appearance: .emphasized, shape: .rounded, size: .default)","    \/\/ Or also","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\")","    \/\/ Or from a localizale and a bundle","    OUDSTag(LocalizedStringKey(\"label_wording\"), bundle: Bundle.module)","","    \/\/ Tag with neutral status with bullet","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(leading: .bullet)","","    \/\/ Tag with neutral status with a custom decorative icon","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\")))","    \/\/ If your layout is in RTL mode but your tag has an icon with another meaning because of bad orientation,","    \/\/ you can flip the icon","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"), flipIcon: true))","","    \/\/ Text with neutral status with bullet","    OUDSTag(label: \"Label\", status: .neutral(bullet: true))","","    \/\/ Tag with loader with rounded shape in small size","    OUDSTag(loadingLabel: \"Label\", shape: .rounded, size: .small)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"anchor":"Design-documentation","text":"Design documentation","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-tag","isActive":true}]},{"anchor":"Themes-rendering","text":"Themes rendering","type":"heading","level":2},{"anchor":"Orange","text":"Orange","type":"heading","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tag_Orange"}]},{"anchor":"Orange-Compact","text":"Orange Compact","type":"heading","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tag_OrangeCompact"}]},{"anchor":"Sosh","text":"Sosh","type":"heading","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tag_Sosh"}]},{"anchor":"Wireframe","text":"Wireframe","type":"heading","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_tag_Wireframe"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.4.0 (Figma component design version)"}]}],"name":"Version","type":"aside","style":"note"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.18.0"}]}],"name":"Since","type":"aside","style":"note"}]}],"references":{"component_tag_Wireframe":{"identifier":"component_tag_Wireframe","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_tag_Wireframe.png"}],"alt":"A tag component in light and dark modes with Wireframe theme","type":"image"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSTag/Size":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSTag\/Size","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Size","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudstag\/size","fragments":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Size","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Defines the size of an "},{"typ